1. Sign into the Azure portal.

2. Click the + Create a resource button, search for Azure AI Search, and create a Azure AI Search resource with the following settings:

   Subscription: Your Azure subscription.
   Resource group: Select or create a resource group with a unique name.
   Service name: A unique name.
   Location: Choose any available region.
   Pricing tier: Basic
   Select Review + create, and after you see the response Validation Success, select Create.

3. After deployment completes, select Go to resource. On the Azure AI Search overview page, you can add indexes, import data, and search created indexes.
